Converse Eyewear 2021

Author: Pelle

Created using free AD WebGL Export for Rhino version 2014.1.0.15108.

Usage:

  • Double click left mouse button to show this help / click to hide.
  • Hold left mouse button to rotate.
  • Hold left mouse button and SHIFT or CTRL key to pan.
  • Use mouse wheel or middle button to zoom in/out.
  • Click to start/reverse turn table.
